{"tid":1396561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3名男子涉網上發布煽惑他人信息及公布警員資料被捕","createTime":"2019-08-02T06:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:14:59.000Z","uid":53003,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c3373902703495488253a9f233628c6040155d31","tid":1396561,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"3名男子涉嫌在網絡上發布煽動他人犯罪的信息，及公布警務人員的個人資料，在過去3日內分別被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n網絡安全及科技罪案調查科警司莫俊傑說，收到警務人員的舉報，警方經調查後發現有人在各社交網站，公布警務人員及他們家人的個人資料，對他們造成滋擾，亦有呼籲其他網民圍堵建築物。有被捕人士使用警務人員的資料，在網上申請貸款，但不成功。<br />\n<br />\n莫俊傑說，警方留意到近日網上有言論，指導他人製作攻擊性武器、爆炸品等，他提醒市民，不要被激進言論煽動，網絡世界亦有法可依。<br />\n<br />\n3名被補男子年齡介乎26至39歲，其中2人涉嫌干犯煽惑他人進行公眾妨擾罪，另外1人涉嫌欺詐罪被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方在行動中檢獲2部電腦及5部電話，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472088-20190802.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472088-20190802.htm&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=86dd3288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472088-20190802.htm&h=281cc2e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472088-20190802.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ce2b85fc1fd6e20df4d1bef8ee902171a90aa307","tid":1396561,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"有條咁嘅罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b206c5c0a44d0b8e01ab6cefab282dba16d4dbf6","tid":1396561,"uid":66324,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"ce2b85fc1fd6e20df4d1bef8ee902171a90aa307","tid":1396561,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"有條咁嘅罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"香港版尋釁滋事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48e04f880765af92e794b4